===Etymology===
From an old Chinese fable.

===Proverb===
[[Category:Japanese proverbs]]
'''船頭多くして船山に登る''' (せんどうおおくしてふねやまにのぼる, sendō ōkushite fune yama ni noboru)

#[[Too many cooks spoil the broth]]. ''Lit.'' "The boat is climbing a mountain with many skippers."

